title: Person With Skullcap Dark Skin Tone
description: A person wearing a skullcap, depicted with a dark skin tone. It can represent cultural or religious identity, or simply a person with a specific hairstyle.

The cap is rendered with Apple's signature soft rounded edges and subtle shading, suggesting a comfortable, close fit.  A gentle, neutral expression is conveyed, making this emoji ideal for representing a person of faith, contemplation, or simply someone sporting a stylish headwear choice with a touch of cultural significance on Apple devices.
